    <div class="header" id="header">
<a name='toptopSTVIRTVaT' id='toptopSTVIRTVaT'></a><h1>GNN北京之行</h1>
<h2>与巨牛们共处</h2>
</div>

<div class="toc" id="toc">
  <ol>
  <li><a href="#toc1R0VYQ0FSM">GNN北京交流</a>
    <ul>
    <li><a href="#toc2R0VYRENMU">1.1. 现场</a>
    </li>
    <li><a href="#toc3R0VYREVMU">1.2. 照片</a>
    </li>
    <li><a href="#toc4R0VYREdMU">1.3. 感想</a>
