  <content>
    <div class="header" id="header">
<a name='toptopTE5VR0NZM' id='toptopTE5VR0NZM'></a><h1>[hack5]样式！</h1>
<h2>颜色系统...FT!</h2>
<h3>t2t渲染:2010-10-09 02:21:38</h3>
</div>

<div class="toc" id="toc">
  <ol>
  <li><a href="#toc1R0VYQ0IyR">设计</a>
